H.B. 527
GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF NORTH CAROLINA
Mar 26, 2025
SESSION 2025
HOUSE PRINCIPAL CLERK
H D
HOUSE BILL DRH10185-LGa-132
Short Title: Funds for Swansboro Rd Maintenance. (Public)
Sponsors: Representative Gable.
Referred to:
1 A BILL TO BE ENTITLED
2 AN ACT TO APPROPRIATE FUNDS TO THE TOWN OF SWANSBORO FOR ROAD
3 MAINTENANCE.
4 The General Assembly of North Carolina enacts:
5 SECTION 1. There is appropriated from the General Fund to the Office of State
6 Budget and Management the sum of two million dollars ($2,000,000) to provide a directed grant
7 to the Town of Swansboro for road maintenance.
8 SECTION 2. This act becomes effective July 1, 2025.
*DRH10185-LGa-132*

